   SUMMAGRAPHICS Corp. (Seymour, Conn.) -- Two vice
presidents were named senior vice presidents in connection
with the acquisition of the Houston Instrument division of
Ametek Inc. William J. Greene became senior vice president,
chief financial officer and treasurer. Robert B. Sims became
senior vice president, secretary and general counsel. In
addition, Paul D. Smith, senior vice president, chief
technical officer, will now supervise all technical aspects
of four newly created divisions of the computer peripheral
products maker.
